5.The price variable appears to have some extreme values. Remove the outliers in the “price” variable using the IQR method. IQR and quantile functions throw error if you have NAs in your variable. Use na.rm=TRUE option inside IQR and quantile methods to ignore the missing price values.

IQR <- IQR(data$price,na.rm=TRUE)
